    <TD colspan="2">The XNAT Team has developed an XNAT compliant DICOM C-Store Service Class Provider, called DICOM Server. It will receive any DICOM compliant data and store it in the prearchive or archive space dependent on project settings.  XNAT provides a built in JAVA applet which can send files directly to this client.  The XNAT Team has also built a java-based DICOM client tool (DICOM Browser) which will view, modify, anonymize and send DICOM data to any DICOM C-Store Provider (particularly DICOM Server).</TD>
